Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.78,0:01:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.25,0:01:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.55,0:01:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安，我是來接ちぃ的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.85,0:01:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.82,0:01:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.99,0:01:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.09,0:01:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.73,0:02:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.73,0:02:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，慢一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.30,0:02:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.77,0:02:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是ちぃ一個人做的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.08,0:02:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是ちぃ做的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.71,0:02:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她學得很快\N所以我就讓她做看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.38,0:02:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果就做出這麼漂亮的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.18,0:02:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好厲害喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.15,0:02:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.82,0:02:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不嫌棄的話\N就吃一口看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.52,0:02:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.89,0:02:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.93,0:02:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就吃一塊看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.27,0:02:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.44,0:02:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.50,0:02:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.17,0:02:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.91,0:02:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個真是太好吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.21,0:02:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人的感情真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.55,0:02:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.69,0:03:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#18         ちぃ，不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.93,0:03:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，連蛋糕都會做了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.43,0:03:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.83,0:03:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.73,0:03:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我如果教我家這台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道她會不會做點小菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.51,0:03:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說\N這真是個了不起的發明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.41,0:03:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長得像人，而且又可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.91,0:03:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管說什麼都乖巧的聽從
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.95,0:03:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還能應付大部分的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.62,0:03:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長，啤酒來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.65,0:03:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我搬到後面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.62,0:03:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.86,0:03:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得裕美妳也有台電腦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.99,0:03:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，有一台小的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.53,0:03:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前我也有一台人型  的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.97,0:03:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻越用越傷心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.14,0:03:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然電腦的確什麼都辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.11,0:03:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且比人還要優秀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.88,0:03:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人覺得電腦比人要好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過如此一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.68,0:04:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人就不能待在人的身邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.19,0:04:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聊這麼奇怪的話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.03,0:04:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.17,0:04:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人就不能待在人的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.98,0:04:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人與電腦…啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上了，早上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.78,0:05:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經天亮了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.81,0:05:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.75,0:05:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.98,0:05:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.19,0:05:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也提起精神來做早操吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.56,0:05:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼每天早上都會被嚇到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.59,0:05:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也該習慣了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.43,0:05:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦，她只是電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.04,0:05:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.28,0:05:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得很起勁喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.45,0:05:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是腳部運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.29,0:05:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.46,0:05:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇洛如那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.73,0:05:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放學後我要去圖書館一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天沒辦法去接妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就一個人回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.47,0:06:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.37,0:06:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很累嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.31,0:06:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早操做太累了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.11,0:06:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不完全是因為那個啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是生病了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.25,0:06:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦\N因為早上受到太大的刺激…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.59,0:06:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.57,0:06:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的，我沒有生病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.70,0:06:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，所以放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.44,0:06:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.68,0:06:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.98,0:06:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的…太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.89,0:06:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到秀樹可能生病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就突然覺得胸口好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出門的時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.78,0:07:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快奔出房門吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.13,0:07:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.51,0:07:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.11,0:07:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，ちぃ不但很照顧我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且看來也很擔心的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.52,0:07:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之她真的很…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.28,0:07:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且比人還要優秀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.02,0:08:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人覺得電腦比人要好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.47,0:08:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的老公變得只跟電腦說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.84,0:08:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師的老公也迷上了電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.28,0:08:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候只是覺得\N這種事很不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近這種事情越來越多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.55,0:08:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ真的很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.62,0:08:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著ちぃ的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.96,0:08:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但心跳得很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.43,0:08:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還會很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.00,0:08:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，她並不是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.57,0:08:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越來越覺得ちぃ不只是台電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.37,0:08:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟把ちぃ當成什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.79,0:09:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人就不能待在人的身邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.07,0:09:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ得趕快去打工，不要遲到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.75,0:09:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（漸漸的         沒有任何人的小鎮）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那本書的續集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.72,0:10:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，完全搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.89,0:10:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人與電腦間會怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.39,0:10:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重考生哪來的時間思考這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.70,0:10:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，下次再想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.77,0:10:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且再拖下去的話\Nちぃ一定又會擔心我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.91,0:10:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.78,0:10:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.15,0:10:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工應該早就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電話，有電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.93,0:10:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快接電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.16,0:10:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.19,0:10:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次請稔教我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.56,0:10:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把家裡的電話\N都轉到絲茉茉這邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.70,0:10:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快接電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.77,0:10:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我接過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.17,0:10:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.97,0:11:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉這麼晚還打電話過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.14,0:11:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問是本須和公館嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.11,0:11:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,植田店長？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.41,0:11:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是本須和吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.81,0:11:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好我也要找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.78,0:11:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.82,0:11:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天她沒來店裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.52,0:11:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很擔心她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.29,0:11:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以打電話問一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.82,0:11:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她沒去你那邊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.59,0:11:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.90,0:11:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.83,0:11:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.93,0:11:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再打給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.04,0:11:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐，管理員小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.08,0:11:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.65,0:11:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.18,0:12:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到處都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.08,0:12:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會又像上次偷窺小屋那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.21,0:12:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碰上什麼麻煩事了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.13,0:13:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是上次來買這套畫冊的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.23,0:13:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟那台長頭髮的電腦女孩一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.80,0:13:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.27,0:13:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天上午\N她還在這裡看過這本書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.47,0:13:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她每次都會來買新的續集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我想要叫住她時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.08,0:13:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不知道跑到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.15,0:13:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.05,0:13:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且書好像也少了一本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.85,0:13:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.02,0:13:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛我在店門口撿到這個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.51,0:13:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ沒見過的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是秀樹的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.64,0:14:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳被綁架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.08,0:14:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綁架？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，妳被綁票了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.02,0:14:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳被誘拐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.09,0:14:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被綁票了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.06,0:14:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是好料的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.10,0:14:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是說相聲裡負責裝傻的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.67,0:14:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.84,0:14:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是好事？還是壞事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.90,0:14:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是什麼都不懂耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.91,0:15:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ有很多事情都不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.64,0:15:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以秀樹教我很多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.18,0:15:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹撿到了ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.92,0:15:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把ちぃ帶到他的房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹會教ちぃ好多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然是那台電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.73,0:15:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.24,0:15:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小島良由起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.04,0:15:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小島…良由起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.41,0:15:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我良由起就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.41,0:15:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.71,0:15:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.35,0:15:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,良由起的房間？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.01,0:15:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.55,0:15:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼“這個”啊\N真沒禮貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是有名字的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.23,0:15:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫琴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ記起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“這個”是琴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.77,0:15:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫妳不要叫我“這個”嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的是什麼都不懂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.51,0:16:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ被綁架到這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.51,0:16:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綁架啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.01,0:16:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次聽到妳的事情以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.09,0:16:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就一直想著妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.16,0:16:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於讓我找到妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.49,0:16:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在書店看到妳的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.43,0:16:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一眼就認出是妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.47,0:16:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我要好好的調查妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.07,0:16:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳應該是很特別的才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.74,0:16:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，也許真的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是Chobits系列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ是Chobits？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.05,0:16:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.55,0:16:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ就是ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹幫我取的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.39,0:16:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼叫ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.12,0:16:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為ちぃ一開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.39,0:16:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只會說“ちぃ”這個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.00,0:17:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是\N幫小貓小狗取的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.44,0:17:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之我會好好幫妳驗明正身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.08,0:17:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟琴子說就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.28,0:17:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，待會見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.93,0:17:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ是秀樹幫我取的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹幫我取的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.27,0:17:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡這個名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.05,0:18:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.02,0:18:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經答應那個人\N什麼都不做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.87,0:18:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情變得越來越離奇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.58,0:19:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管我怎麼查這張圖片的來源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.19,0:19:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是在中途就卡住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來對方真的很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.93,0:19:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在非常對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的硬體性能不夠好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.86,0:19:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以幫不上您的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.77,0:19:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是柚姬的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.77,0:19:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的經驗不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.84,0:19:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.97,0:19:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了幫助稔少爺\N才做出來的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.01,0:19:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻辦不到您所吩咐的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.52,0:19:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.28,0:19:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳幫了我很多忙啊，柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.59,0:19:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫了我太多\N讓我不知該如何是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.73,0:19:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次稔少爺傷心的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.93,0:19:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您姊姊總是會這樣抱著您，對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.57,0:19:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.14,0:19:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從上次維修以後\N就沒再更新過姊姊的資料了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.17,0:20:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓我變得更像您的姊姊\N請您輸入新的資料吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.55,0:20:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於您姊姊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.09,0:20:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.09,0:20:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.59,0:20:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰打來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.76,0:20:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.96,0:20:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.10,0:20:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.10,0:20:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.87,0:20:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔，ちぃ不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她突然不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.94,0:20:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來事情蠻嚴肅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.07,0:20:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼線索嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.31,0:20:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的髮箍掉在書店門口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.61,0:20:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆說她突然就消失不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.15,0:20:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找過很多地方\N不過就是找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.98,0:20:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保也不在\N這個時候我只能找你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.09,0:20:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我有種不好的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了，我馬上過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.59,0:20:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到多卡利昂等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通話完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.37,0:20:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出門吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.07,0:21:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許會有些非調查不可的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳願意陪我一起去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.51,0:21:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.68,0:21:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次跟我出去的時候\N柚姬總是會這樣笑著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.25,0:21:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我可以陪在稔少爺的身邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.79,0:21:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.69,0:21:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.77,0:21:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.67,0:21:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的老公變得只跟電腦說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.51,0:21:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得電腦比較可愛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.18,0:21:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和人類比起來\N跟電腦在一起比較快樂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.95,0:21:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人就不能待在人的身邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.82,0:21:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何，一定得找到ちぃ才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.39,0:21:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.53,0:21:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，千萬別出事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.14,0:22:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚的街道如同深海般寂靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.05,0:22:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綿延的路上卻只有我孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.23,0:22:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,循著遠方的聲音向前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.30,0:23:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷找尋著一閃即逝的藍色光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.99,0:23:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.53,0:23:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後不再遺忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.44,0:23:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使有多心痛         也要在你身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.12,0:23:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到永遠         直到永遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.83,0:23:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如，我搞丟了一個錢包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.57,0:23:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是被我搞丟的錢包\N卻不會感到不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.47,0:23:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不會覺得孤單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.54,0:23:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管皮包裡裝著什麼東西\N我也不會擔心那個皮包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.31,0:23:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ是台電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.05,0:23:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定也不會感到不安或是孤單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.02,0:24:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.38,0:24:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是很擔心ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.05,0:24:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits         下一回\N「ちぃ，等待」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.46,0:24:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是怎麼了
